{"tid":1961956,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同意要長遠抵制黨鐵 一定要逼巴士公司加密班次","createTime":"2020-04-07T06:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T17:37:23.000Z","uid":40431,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d8c8ced598bc41089f36b8002bce69b93d2c927","tid":1961956,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"平時黨鐵疏極，1-5分鐘一定有一班，巴士最密係過海線，其他多數10-20分一班<br />\n<br />\n而家武漢肺炎，黨鐵減完班都5分鐘有車，巴士有啲疏到半粒鐘先一班<br />\n<br />\n遲啲如果沙中線通晒車，肯定再cut多啲巴士，路線重疊嘅巴士線一定減班，分分鐘取消埋，因為港共咁多年嚟交通發展都係谷人坐黨鐵，睇吓馬鞍山就知<br />\n<br />\n到時仲叫香港人罷搭黨鐵就變到好離地，time is money，出去食飯或者玩嘅都話唔介意等耐啲，返工返學如果仲叫人等半個鐘仲要未必上到車 (班次疏+繁忙時間多人搭巴士)，我肯你肯連登仔肯，其他人都未必肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以如果長遠要罷鐵，一定要多啲向區議員反映巴士太疏，或者直接向巴士公司投訴 (不過經驗話我知投訴冇乜效)，班次密啲先吸引到多啲人放棄黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n如果有同感或者有其他方法覺得更加有用，不妨一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751f3174d9331a34d2d6e89d4e920bd4d70e3257","tid":1961956,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:48:24.000Z","msg":"無力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6ac1377b03042e93de7b7f3adc924c01e14adc","tid":1961956,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a3a2a6cb1e81dace3f144acc6077cbea17bf3af","tid":1961956,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7554070067667ccf8c909f2e91989e8ed196889","tid":1961956,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eed8d76d75d3ba175b061e39d3085afa83bdd09","tid":1961956,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:5